Pirelli May Purchase Assets in Far East, Tronchetti Tells Sole

-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i
-- 
2011-07-28T05:47:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/pirelli-may-purchase-assets-in-far-east-tronchetti-tells-sole.html
Pirelli & C. SpA may purchase assets
in the  Far East  if opportunities arise, Chairman Marco
Tronchetti Provera was quoted as saying by  Il Sole 24 Ore .  Tronchetti, who ruled out full company acquisitions,
expects to double production in the region by 2014, the
executive was cited as saying by Sole.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sonia Sirletti in Milan at 
 ssirletti@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net  